🔍 A) Product Search – Test Cases

TC1: Valid Product Search (Positive)
Steps: Enter "The Collection Snowboard: Liquid" in search bar → Click search
Expected Result: Product card/page for "The Collection Snowboard: Liquid" is displayed

TC2: Partial Keyword Search (Positive)
Steps: Enter "Snowboard" → Click search
Expected Result: Products containing "Snowboard" are displayed, including "The Collection Snowboard: Liquid"

TC3: Invalid Product Search (Negative)
Steps: Enter "abc123xyz" → Click search
Expected Result: "No products found" message is displayed

TC4: Empty Search (Edge Case)
Steps: Leave search bar empty → Click search
Expected Result: Either all products displayed or validation message appears

TC5: Special Characters Search (Negative)
Steps: Enter "@#$%" → Click search
Expected Result: No results displayed or proper validation message shown

TC6: Case Insensitivity Check (Edge Case)
Steps: Search "THE COLLECTION SNOWBOARD: LIQUID" → Search "the collection snowboard: liquid"
Expected Result: Both searches return the same results
